Show HN: Cosmic Basin – Free and beautiful AI-generated images for your website
text:
Hi HN, I made Cosmic Basin after I got frustrated with how hard it was to discover high quality AI art that I could use for my side projects.

I think AI art will play a big role of visual content in the future, and many of the images generated today are more than high quality enough to use as wallpapers, splash images, OG images, and more.

All of the images can be used / downloaded for free on personal and commercial projects. I am hoping to add more high quality images every day to slowly grow the collection.

I believe that "AI artists" will be a profession in the future, and I hope long term, Cosmic Basin could be a community for people who want to discover and share AI art. Here's some more info on why I built the site: https://www.cosmicbasin.com/about.

Show HN: Perfectacademia.com – Crowd-sourced reviews and ratings of universities
text:
Introducing, PerfectAcademia.com — Crowd-sourced reviews and ratings platform for universities all over the world.

- 9700+ universities - 204 countries - Anonymous reviews

---

# Why?

The aim of this platform is to help students make an informed decision about choosing colleges.

If you're looking for a new university, this is your go-to resource for learning about them in depth.

---

# How?

The initial data was loaded from https://github.com/Hipo/university-domains-list.

Then the platform was build using, Framework → Remix.run Styling/Primitives → TailwindCSS, HeadlessUI & Radix UI DB → Prisma w/ CockroachDB Hosting → Vercel
